Final Overall Wiring Plan (L0–L3)

North Star: What “Fully Wired” Means

A feature is not done unless this loop works end-to-end:

Connect → Ingest → Normalize → Link (Truth+Context) → Score vs Goals (Dual-context) → Propose → Approve → Execute → Learn → Update UI

And the UI rule holds:
	•	L1 shows only facts + goal-linked state
	•	L2 shows reasoning, evidence, proposals, approvals
	•	No writes without approval

