Phase 0 — Foundations (Hard Requirements)

0.1 Tenancy + Identity (L0)
	•	tenant_id propagation everywhere
	•	user identity + session validation
	•	org/persona mapping (exec/manager/ic/admin)

0.2 RBAC + Policy Baseline (cross-cutting, enforced in L0 + L2 + L3)
	•	roles/scopes for: read, propose, approve, execute
	•	per-connector write scopes (e.g., Slack post allowed, Salesforce update needs approval)
	•	audit logging enabled by default

0.3 Canonical IDs + Traceability (L3 contract)
	•	entity_id (stable SSOT identity)
	•	trace_id per ingest event
	•	lineage pointers for every field
	•	DLQ + replay pointer for failures

Definition of Done
	•	Every request includes tenant_id
	•	Every action has trace_id and lands in audit

