Wiring

L1 “Sync Now”
→ L0 reads token from vault
→ provider fetch (contacts/deals/companies)
→ POST batch to Loader
→ store last_sync_at, counts, errors

L0 additions
	•	token refresh utility
	•	sync history records

Definition of Done
