Phase 3 — L3 Real Pipeline (8-stage Loader + NA0–NA5 Normalizer)

Goal: Raw data becomes SSOT truth + linked context.

L3: Loader (8 stages)
	•	fingerprint + idempotency table
	•	classifier + domain routing
	•	filtering (PII rules, quota, validation)
	•	refinement (split entities, normalize fields)
	•	extractor (canonical mapping)
	•	validator (required fields + warnings)
	•	write plan (Spine vs Context vs Audit)
	•	writers (Spine upsert + context write + emit Think queue)

L3: Normalizer (NA0–NA5)
	•	schema detection
	•	canonical transformation
	•	SSOT binding (stable identity)
	•	lineage recording
	•	relationship binding
	•	dual-write: Spine (Truth) + Context (Knowledge)

Definition of Done
	•	duplicate payload rejected by idempotency
	•	entities appear in Spine with entity_id
	•	context items link to entity_id
	•	audit + lineage exist for the write

