Phase 4 — Webhook → Pipeline Bridge (Real-time Events)

Goal: Webhooks from tools flow into Loader/Normalizer.

Wiring

Provider webhook
→ Gateway route (keeps raw audit copy)
→ fire-and-forget Loader ingest
→ DLQ on failure

Definition of Done
	•	Stripe/Slack/HubSpot webhook creates/upserts entities in Spine
	•	failures land in DLQ with replay option

